2014-09-13  rocky <rocky@gnu.org>

	* .gitignore, command/info_sub/Makefile.am, configure.ac,
	doc/notecase-HTML.sh, init/require.sh, lib/file.sh, lib/frame.sh,
	test/integration/.gitignore, test/integration/Makefile.am,
	test/integration/test-file-with-spaces,
	test/integration/test-file-with-spaces.in, test/unit/Makefile.am,
	test/unit/test-get-sourceline.sh.in: tilde expansion reinstated,
	some embedded blank in filenames reinstated. These had been broken
	by changes in bash 4.3. Get ready for release 0.9 .gitignore: more ignore for new test autoconf generation
	command/info_sub/Makefile.am: remove dup directory configure.ac: the
	way to pass PIC for set0 has changed. get ready for release 0.9
	lib/file.sh: adjust tilde expansion for bash 4.3 lib/frame.sh: add
	missing _Dbg_frame_file test/integration/Makefile.am: remove some
	fancy GNU functions not_dir and wildcard
	test/integration/test-file-with-spaces.in: reinstate test
	test/unit/test-get-sourceline.sh.in: reinstate test

