2006-12-26  rockyb <rockyb>

	* dbg-list.inc: Don't linetrace if depth < 0; this removes that
	bashdb call lines.  Use last_command on string substitution, not source line. That way
	we don't have problems of mismatched quotes and such.  This is subtle, because the source line is what (not the command) is
	really what we want in showing location info.

